{"name":"Serpent Staff","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-forest-jewel.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 6 Catalyst &bull; Psychic, Divine</strong></p>\n<p><em>A staff shaped like a winding snake, carved from green-lacquered wood and topped with a glowing green gemstone held between the serpent's teeth. An eerie power emanates from it.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Reliquary</strong> World Serpent<br><strong>Domains&nbsp;</strong>Life, Poison, Serpent<br><strong>Will&nbsp;</strong>8<br><strong>Favor&nbsp;</strong>3</p>\n<p><strong>Psychic </strong>The <em>Serpent Staff&nbsp;</em>is also a psychic catalyst, granting a +4 equipment bonus to manifesting Psychic powers, and a +7 bonus to manifesting Fate powers.<br><strong>Mana Toxin </strong>Powers manifested using this staff apply a -3 penalty to attempts to counterspell them. When a power is a successfully manifested through this catalyst, the wielder gains an Aura 10 until the beginning of their next turn; attempts to cast Arcane spells in this aura gain a -4 penalty.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":5,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"3d10+18","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":17,"quantity":null,"subType":"Staff"},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9VLaNZ1lPpgeGT4f"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1772770112341,"modifiedTime":1774718817009,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"gttITde40wukfBJx"}
{"name":"Moonray","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-ornate-teal.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 6 Legendary Staff &bull; Arcane, Cold, Moonlight</strong></p>\n<p><em>Legendary staff of Iyalan, cast from millions of strands of solid moonlight. The staff is cold to the touch and smooth like glass, emanating a faint silver glow.</em></p>\n<p><em>Moonray</em> is a <em>+2 Resonating Manabind</em> <em>Staff</em>. It has the following characteristics:</p>\n<p><strong>Solid</strong> <strong>Moonlight:&nbsp;</strong>Moonray grants a +4 bonus to casting arcane spells. This bonus increases to +7 for Ice and Moonlight spells.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Resonating:&nbsp;</strong>Moonray becomes more efficient at channeling magical energy with every spell it casts in quick succession. For every spell channeled through&nbsp;<em>Moonray&nbsp;</em>on a given turn, its casting bonuses increase by 1, up to a maximum of +6/+9.</p>\n<p><strong>Manabind:&nbsp;</strong>Moonray grants a +6 bonus to counterspelling. If&nbsp;<em>Moonray&nbsp;</em>is used to perform a successful counterspell, the wielder recovers Focus equal to the cost of the countered spell.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","bulk":1,"charge":4,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"2d8+27","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":18,"quantity":null,"subType":"Staff"},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gatmEqjgdTNbEJJs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768049056439,"modifiedTime":1774718836255,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"6G4xRHlxy1E2mFPy"}
{"name":"Memento Mori","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/equipment/neck/necklace-carved-bone-skull.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 4 Psychic Catalyst &bull; Time, Fate</strong></p>\n<p><em>An amulet carved in the form of a miniature human skull. The Dark-Elven inscription reads 'Remember thou, o mage, that one day thou, too, shalt face oblivion'.&nbsp;</em></p>\n<p>The <em>Memento Mori </em>grants its wielder a +2 equipment bonus to manifesting Psychic powers. The bonus increases to +5 for Time and Fate powers.</p>","bulk":0,"charge":2,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"2d8+8","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":11,"quantity":null,"subType":"amulet"},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EOSECOxz68iPHXbl"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769894089494,"modifiedTime":1774718839975,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"W4nV3H7ZZiL1Prqi"}
{"name":"Caesium Rod","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-carved-stone-shard.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Catalyst, Tier 5 &bull; Time</strong></p>\n<p><em>A rod of radioactive caesium, encased in a protective sheet of rune-etched lead glass. The resonance of the metal core enhances this catalyst's power in manifesting Time powers.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Resonant Frequency&nbsp;</strong>This rod grants the wielder a +3 equipment bonus to manifesting psychic powers, increasing to +6 for Time powers.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":3,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d10+23","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":16,"quantity":null,"subType":"rod"},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Zd5ea6JqVpsLMWIv"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769893571534,"modifiedTime":1774718841576,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"VhgQchCZLOVU2cfK"}
{"name":"Blackbone Staff","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-animal-skull-bull.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Rn9YWMOa1bQMZ1o7"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This staff was exquisitely carved out of blackened bones and topped with a cast-iron skull inlaid with jewels. It exudes an unearthly chill.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Effects.&nbsp;</strong>This staff grants a +2 bonus to cast Necromancy spells.</p>\n<p><strong>As a Ritual implement. </strong>This staff can be used as a ritual implement with Aspects Scarab 2, Skull 2. It grants a +2 bonus to occultism checks for Necromancy rituals.</p>","bulk":0.5,"charge":1.5,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d8+9","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":9,"quantity":null,"subType":"Staff"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774718843554,"modifiedTime":1774718843554,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"LKfsJuKlQJf7Yj6U"}
{"name":"Blackbone Staff","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-animal-skull-bull.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Rn9YWMOa1bQMZ1o7"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This staff was exquisitely carved out of blackened bones and topped with a cast-iron skull inlaid with jewels. It exudes an unearthly chill.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Effects.&nbsp;</strong>This staff grants a +2 bonus to cast Necromancy spells.</p>\n<p><strong>As a Ritual implement. </strong>This staff can be used as a ritual implement. It grants a +2 bonus to occultism checks for Necromancy rituals.</p>","bulk":0.5,"charge":1.5,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d8+9","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":9,"quantity":null,"subType":"Staff"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774718843554,"modifiedTime":1774718882210,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"LKfsJuKlQJf7Yj6U"}
{"name":"Polybind Staff","type":"catalyst","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-orante-gold.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.plt4k9AqQvD21gDs"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p>This golden staff shimmers with all colors of the rainbow.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Effects.&nbsp;</strong>This staff grants a +3 bonus to cast Summoning spells.</p>\n<p><strong>As a Ritual implement. </strong>This staff can be used as a ritual implement. It grants a +3 bonus to ritual checks for Binding rituals.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":2.5,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d10+12","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":11,"quantity":null,"subType":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774718916724,"modifiedTime":1774718916724,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"aevHtt0G9Am8UFez"}
